==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Australize
<hw>Aus"tral*ize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Austral</er>.]</ety> <def>To tend toward the south pole, as a
magnet.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They [magnets] do septentrionate at one extreme, and
<qex>australize</qex> at another.</q> <rj><qau>Sir T.
Browne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>australopithecine</ent>⟦br⟧
